{"tid":510432,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人飲食口味好老","createTime":"2017-12-26T13:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T02:23:55.000Z","uid":133304,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4f635b1b8ed43a3c75c2e7370a5660956769e3d8","tid":510432,"uid":133304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"除咗之前個post話唔食得甜嘢之餘<br />\n飲唔到凍飲，覺得傷胃（或者飲完即刻飲返熱水中和）<br />\n太鹹都唔鍾意，已經慢慢接受唔到煙肉火腿嗰種鹹<br />\n。<br />\n反而識欣賞苦瓜種微苦<br />\n食嘢prefer清淡或者簡單啲嘅煮法，例如蒸或者烚<br />\n我年齡仲一字頭，成日比人話食嘢口味成個阿伯咁"},{"pid":"6f27e8df5dc2b7cbb68faa37ff6f0ea66b380c77","tid":510432,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"反差萌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455cd85f963a67db2eda99e3ce4b88181cdb8f89","tid":510432,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"型<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46a387e8e45d20f512d18f49edab6d45554b4f4","tid":510432,"uid":133304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>型<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可惜現實樣子和身形不是<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b58fed4b2bcc3701778d6780f1ad5fbb0231668","tid":510432,"uid":154255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T14:20:43.000Z","msg":"咁咪好，夠健康<br />\n起碼無咁易病，以前都食好多炸野<br />\n全部飲凍飲，身體越來越差<br />\n之後依家都食好清淡，同習慣左飲熱飲"},{"pid":"41e406cef714e82e295819f9564f6820689ee93d","tid":510432,"uid":89252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔食甜野<br />\n唔飲凍野<br />\n只飲暖水<br />\n一年四季都帶暖水壺出街<br />\n<br />\n甜野凍野本身好鐘意食<br />\n係中醫叫戒嘅<br />\n身體係好左d<br />\n<br />\n長年飲暖水係因為自己覺得暖水好飲d <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知關唔關氣管敏感事<br />\n不過年年夏天拎個暖水壺出嚟都覺得自己好奇怪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7552c5cd89ddfe411c6efa8424aae1b3bad608d4","tid":510432,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:36:43.000Z","msg":"古早味花生糖"},{"pid":"54792caf81897e593d13aa48aaaac3f1c37dd0a3","tid":510432,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:06:23.000Z","msg":"我出街鐘意食蒸魚炒菜果啲，好多人食火鍋放題果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e091c0100bdbb435f8c77449d99d4b02aec7e1bb","tid":510432,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:23:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}